  "_postman_id": "cbs-full-api-suite-v1",
  "name": "Content Broadcasting System — Full API Suite",
  "description": "Complete test suite: all endpoints, happy paths, validation errors, RBAC enforcement, scheduling edge cases.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. `npm run seed` — creates default users in DB\n2. Run ** Auth → Login as Principal** and **Login as Teacher 1** first — they auto-save tokens\n3. For upload requests, click the `file` row and pick any local JPG/PNG/GIF\n4. Run the full collection in order via Collection Runner for the complete E2E flow\n\n## Seeded Credentials\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| Principal | principal@school.com | Principal@123 |\n| Teacher 1 | teacher1@school.com | Teacher@123 |\n| Teacher 2 | teacher2@school.com | Teacher@123 |\n\n## Notes\nThis is a lean suite with core endpoints. Edge-case checks are intentionally centralized under the \"Security & Edge Cases\" folder.",
